snippet.title: MINTROCKET: Unveils New Project | Project NAKWON, PvPvE Extraction Survival
snippet.description:
MINTROCKET unveils the gameplay of the new project, [NAKWON].
The Features shown in this video are still in the stage of development, and the outcome may differ.

Project NAKWON is a Third-Person Loot-Extraction Survival multiplayer game for PC that aims to extract and survive from where its unique zombie apocalypse concepts set in.
■ Project NAKWON: https://mintrocketgames.com/en/nakwon
